title: EVELINE COSMETICS SLIM EXTREME 4D INTENSE SERUM REDUCING FATTY TISSUE
description:
Innovative formula, rich in advanced active ingredients acting in synergy with IntenslimTM complex, visibly reduces waist girth and slenderises silhouette. bioHyaluron Slim ComplexTM containing hyaluronic acid intensely moisturises, smoothens and firms. Plant milk Chufa Milk EC, laminaria algae and grape seed oil nourish and invigorate epidermis.

APPLICATION: twice a day vigorously massage the product with circular movements into problematic parts of the body (waist, abdomen, buttocks, thighs) until fully absorbed. Pleasant cooling sensation accompanying application is the guarantee of immediate action of the serum. Wash hands after application.
